		<itunes:summary>(http://www.mymorningstory.com/wp-content/uploads/DamagedSoul.jpg)A blue lady bug so cold so rare warm blood inside. Skin so cold you"ll die. I was only 5 years old when I saw them fight.

My name is chris I will tell you my sad life. My mother Shelle had baby blue eyes just like the sky, Long wavy brown hair as soft as the worlds softest tedy bear, and she was lightskinned. My father Eric had Hazel Brown eyes, Curly black hair and super dark. I was only 5 when I saw them fight. My dad came home drunk and high cussing calling my mom a bitch and a slut. Iv'e never seen them act like this my dad slapped my mom as she started to cry. As I stood there tears fall down my face. The painful feeling inside my mother the one that gave me the best days of my life. I yell at my dad "stop hitting my mom Take your hands off her". I run towards him and I jump on his back. I hit him in the back of the head but my hits have no affect. The next thing I know he grabs me by my arms and throws me hard at the wall.

I start to cry as I spit blood out of my mouth. I was thrown so hard I think I have a broken bone. I get back up and the next thing I see is a glass cup flying towards me. I didn't move fast enough as a piece of glass sticks out my throat and glass sticks out my eye. My mother see's me there is a pool of blood my mom hits him in the back of the head with a wine bottle and runs to my aid. I am barley breathing she rushes me to the hospital.

I am only 8 years old now they say "There is nothing we can do". I have 3 broken ribs one is in my lungs.  My mother cries I cry too. I slowly close my eye's my mother screams " My only son gone out of my life".

